1. Start the Backend (Python)
Open a Terminal.

Type these commands:

Bash

cd backend
python app.py

Start the Frontend (React)
Open a New Terminal (Click the + icon in the terminal panel or press Ctrl + Shift + `).

Type these commands:

Bash

cd frontend
npm run dev

You should see: Local: http://localhost:5173/

Now open http://localhost:5173 in your browser to use the portal.